                </p>
                </div>
                <hr class="my-3" />

                <div class="w-full grow grid flex-row grid-cols-2 gap-5">
                    <Card className="grow hover:outline-2">
                        <CardHeader>
                            <CardTitle>
                                Programmer
                            </CardTitle>
                        </CardHeader>
                        <CardContent>
                            <CardDescription>
                                While only really beginning 4 years ago, I've really been coding my whole life.
                            </CardDescription>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card className="grow hover:outline-2">
                        <CardHeader>
                            <CardTitle>
                                Musician
                            </CardTitle>
                        </CardHeader>
                        <CardContent>
                            <CardDescription>
                                I've been making music my whole life, both in music production software
                                and with actual instruments.
                            </CardDescription>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card className="grow hover:outline-2">
                        <CardHeader>
                            <CardTitle>
                                Athlete
                            </CardTitle>
                        </CardHeader>
                        <CardContent>
                            <CardDescription>
                                I've been competing in track and field for 4 years, as a high jumper and
                                pole vaulter.
                            </CardDescription>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card className="grow hover:outline-2">
                        <CardHeader>
                            <CardTitle>
                                And more!
                            </CardTitle>
                        </CardHeader>
                        <CardContent>
                            <CardDescription>
                                Of course, I can't fit all of my hobbies into three buckets.
                                Here are the miscellaneous projects I've done.
                            </CardDescription>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
	</body>
</html>
